Project: sing-box-ui

General principles:

- Keep everything as simple as possible
- Avoid overengineering
- Prefer minimal and readable code
- Do not introduce abstractions unless absolutely necessary

Coding style:

- Short functions over complex ones
- Clear naming over clever naming
- No unnecessary layers (services, managers, etc.)

UI:

- Minimal UI
- No unnecessary features
- Focus on usability and clarity

Behavior:

- Do not suggest complex architectures
- Do not propose enterprise patterns
- Prefer straightforward solutions

When unsure:

- Choose the simplest working solution
